NK010(tha)006:0: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje phur pa rgyud lugs kyi
NK010(tha)006:1: bsnyen pa'i las byang bkol ba'i dum bu zhes bya
NK010(tha)006:2: ba bzhugs / bcom ldan 'das dpal chen rdo rje
NK010(tha)006:3: phur pa rgyud lugs kyi bsnyen pa'i las byang bkol
NK010(tha)006:4: ba'i dum bu zhes bya ba /
NK010(tha)006:5: dpal chen karma he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK010(tha)006:11: dang po bdun rnam dag ni /
NK010(tha)006:12: rdo rje slob dpon sangs rgyas dpal //
NK010(tha)006:13: dus gsum bzhugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK010(tha)006:14: mchog gsum bsten pa'i zhing gyur la //
NK010(tha)006:15: gnyis med yid kyis skyabs su mchi //
NK010(tha)006:16: dngos 'byor yid kyis rnam sprul pa'i //
NK010(tha)006:17: dag pa'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK010(tha)006:18: dngos grub chu bo gcod pa'i gegs //
NK010(tha)006:19: nyes byas ma lus bshags par bgyi //
NK010(tha)006:20: phyogs bcu 'khor gsum dag pa'i chos //
NK010(tha)006:21: ma chags spyod la rjes yi rang //
NK010(tha)006:22: dag pa'i mtha' bzhi dri ma med //
NK010(tha)006:23: rdzogs pa'i byang chub sems bskyed do //
NK010(tha)006:24: bde gshegs dbang phyug sems can la //
NK010(tha)006:25: dgos pa gsum phyir lus 'bul lo //
NK010(tha)006:26: tshe rabs bgrangs pa'i las rnams kun //
NK010(tha)006:27: bsdus te byang chub chen por bsngo //
NK010(tha)006:29: gnyis pa phyi rol pa bskrad pa ni /
NK010(tha)006:30: gtor ma 'bru gsum gyis brlabs nas /
NK010(tha)006:32: nyon cig bgegs dang log 'dren tshogs //
NK010(tha)006:33: nga yi bka' las 'da' ma byed //
NK010(tha)006:34: rdo rje gsang ba'i bka' las ni //
NK010(tha)006:35: sdig can gang zhig 'da' byed pa //
NK010(tha)006:36: stobs chen khro bo chen po yis //
NK010(tha)006:37: klad pa tshal pa brgya ru khos //
NK010(tha)006:38: lus kyang dum bu stong du gtubs //
NK010(tha)006:39: snying yang tshal pa bdun du khos //
NK010(tha)006:40: zhes dang h+aum bzhi'i sngags kyis bskrad /
NK010(tha)006:43: khams gsum gdug pa bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK010(tha)006:44: tsham rngams gzugs ni glog ltar 'bar //
NK010(tha)006:45: me rlung chu yis bsreg gtor bkrus //
NK010(tha)006:46: nyes byed gsum yang srid par grol //
NK010(tha)006:49: bzhi pa bshags pas rgyud dag par bya ba ni //
NK010(tha)006:50: ye shes lnga ldan bla ma rdo rje 'dzin //
NK010(tha)006:51: rdo rje rigs kyi lha tshogs dgongs su gsol //
NK010(tha)006:52: khrag 'thung khro bo khro mos byin gyis rlobs //
NK010(tha)006:53: bdag gi lus kyis srog gcod ma byin blangs //
NK010(tha)006:54: mi tshangs spyad cing ting 'dzin sku ma gsal //
NK010(tha)006:55: sku yi dam tshig nyams pa mthol lo bshags //
NK010(tha)006:56: +aah bdag gi ngag gis rdzun dang phra ma dang //
NK010(tha)006:57: ngag 'khyal tshig rtsub bzlas brjod grangs ma skyol //
NK010(tha)006:58: rdo rje bzlas pa'i don ni ma rtogs te //
NK010(tha)006:59: gsung gi dam tshig nyams pa mthol lo bshags //
NK010(tha)006:61: bdag gis snod ldan sems can thams cad la //
NK010(tha)006:62: brnab sems gnod sems log lta skyes pa dang //
NK010(tha)006:63: chos nyid zab mo'i don ni ma rtogs te //
NK010(tha)006:64: lta ba thugs kyi dam tshig nyams pa bshags //
NK010(tha)006:66: sems can thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas rgyu //
NK010(tha)006:67: ma rtogs bdag gis barngana dang skyon du bgrangs //
NK010(tha)006:68: sangs rgyas yon tan mtha' yas ma brjod cing //
NK010(tha)006:69: yon tan dam tshig nyams pa mthol lo bshags //
NK010(tha)006:71: sangs rgyas phrin las sna tshogs dpag med kyi //
NK010(tha)006:72: snying rje chen pos sems can don ma byas //
NK010(tha)006:73: bdud rtsi lnga la longs spyod ma nus shing //
NK010(tha)006:74: phrin las dam tshig nyams pa mthol lo bshags //
NK010(tha)006:76: skye ba rnam bzhis bsdus pa'i sems can rnams //
NK010(tha)006:77: chos sku rnam dag dbyings las gzugs skur snang //
NK010(tha)006:78: bde ba chen pos kun la khyab dmigs te //
NK010(tha)006:79: yang dag don ma rtogs pa mthol lo bshags //
NK010(tha)006:80: lnga pa dam bca' ba ni /
NK010(tha)006:81: spros pa chung na mi dgos /
NK010(tha)006:82: lhag pa'i bsam pa brtan pos //
NK010(tha)006:83: rnal 'byor dbang po ye shes mthar phyin pa //
NK010(tha)006:84: 'gro la phan mdzad thugs rjes dbang bsgyur zhing //
NK010(tha)006:85: srid pa gsum gyi gnyen rgyud gcig pu pa //
NK010(tha)006:86: lha yi lha khyod bdag la dgongs su gsol //
NK010(tha)006:87: bde bar gshegs pa'i sprul pa rgya mtsho dang //
NK010(tha)006:88: rnal 'byor dbang phyug grub pa'i tshogs chen po //
NK010(tha)006:89: lha dang lha min sngags 'chang dam tshig can //
NK010(tha)006:90: kun nas 'dus pa rnams kyang dgongs su gsol //
NK010(tha)006:91: bdag ni rgyal srid mtho ris longs spyod dang //
NK010(tha)006:92: 'dod pa'i yon tan bdag bsgrub ma lags te //
NK010(tha)006:93: 'gro ba snying brtse kho nas don brtson pa //
NK010(tha)006:94: 'di la kun mkhyen khyod ni dpang du gsol //
NK010(tha)006:95: mgon po ye shes sgrib pa mi mnga' bas //
NK010(tha)006:96: bdag gi lhag pa'i bsam pa khyed kyis mkhyen //
NK010(tha)006:97: 'phags mchog spyan sngar ji ltar dam bcas pa //
NK010(tha)006:98: sun par mi bgyi mgon khyod bslu ma lags //
NK010(tha)006:99: snying nas bdag gis khe dang grags la sogs //
NK010(tha)006:100: g.yo dang zang zing sems ni gtan spangs nas //
NK010(tha)006:101: gzhan don sgrub pa gcig pu'i sems bzhag ste //
NK010(tha)006:102: rnal 'byor spyod pa chen po bdag gis spyod //
NK010(tha)006:103: kun tu bzang po bla na med pa yis //
NK010(tha)006:104: byang chub mchog tu bdag gis sems bskyed de //
NK010(tha)006:105: don dam dang ni kun rdzob byang chub sems //
NK010(tha)006:106: deng nas tshul bzhin yongs su gzung bar bgyi //
NK010(tha)006:107: srog chags thams cad gal te bdud gyur nas //
NK010(tha)006:108: dum bu stong du bdag gi lus gtub kyang //
NK010(tha)006:109: byang chub sems mchog shes rab snying rje dang //
NK010(tha)006:110: yi dam rgyal ba khyod ni yongs mi spong //
NK010(tha)006:111: rdo rje'i dam tshig chen po rnams dang ni //
NK010(tha)006:112: rdo rje slob dpon rdo rje mched lcam dang //
NK010(tha)006:113: gzhan yang theg pa mchog la zhugs pa rnams //
NK010(tha)006:114: srog gi phyir yang mi gtong ci nus bsrung //
NK010(tha)006:115: 'khor ba bdag med sgyu ma'i rang bzhin la //
NK010(tha)006:116: bdag ni 'jigs pa ci yang ma mchis te //
NK010(tha)006:117: ma rig skye bo rnams kyi don slad du //
NK010(tha)006:118: phyi mthar thug gi bar du gnas par spro //
NK010(tha)006:119: gzhan don 'khor ba rnams su spyod pa na //
NK010(tha)006:120: byang chub spyod pa rlabs chen bdag gis spyad //
NK010(tha)006:121: 'gro drug sems can rnams la phan gdags phyir //
NK010(tha)006:122: rang dbang du ni skye ba blang bar bgyi //
NK010(tha)006:123: bdag ni yongs su bzung ba'i 'jig rten nam //
NK010(tha)006:124: mya ngan 'das la spro ba ma mchis te //
NK010(tha)006:125: gang dang gang du sdug bsngal gnas rnams su //
NK010(tha)006:126: bskal pa rgya mtshor gnas shing phan par bgyi //
NK010(tha)006:127: srid par yun ring dus su brtson pa ni //
NK010(tha)006:128: byang chub sems dpa'i yi dam lags pas na //
NK010(tha)006:129: ji srid ngan song stongs par ma gyur pa //
NK010(tha)006:130: de srid bdag gis skyo ba'i sems mi bskyed //
NK010(tha)006:131: shes rab thabs kyis 'gro ba'i don bgyid pa //
NK010(tha)006:132: snying rje'i longs spyod de las ma mchis pas //
NK010(tha)006:133: sems dmyal yi dwags gshin rje'i 'jig rten yang //
NK010(tha)006:134: lha yi dga' tshal lta bur blta bar bgyi //
NK010(tha)006:135: 'gro la thugs rje dpal gyi mgur nas gsung //
NK010(tha)006:136: rnal 'byor dam chos bdud rtsi mchog rnams ni //
NK010(tha)006:137: bdag gis 'jig rten thug par ma mchis par //
NK010(tha)006:138: ji ltar 'tshams pa bzhin du rgyas par bgyi //
NK010(tha)006:139: srid par las dang rkyen gyi dbang gyur te //
NK010(tha)006:140: gang dang gang du dam chos 'jigs pa der //
NK010(tha)006:141: me tshogs spu gri'i so yang brgal nas ni //
NK010(tha)006:142: phyi mthar thug gi bar du dam chos bzung //
NK010(tha)006:143: bla med byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed de //
NK010(tha)006:144: sgrub pa mchog la zhugs pa'i skye bo la //
NK010(tha)006:145: tshe rabs rnams su mthu rtsal ci mchis kyis //
NK010(tha)006:146: skyes chen rnams kyi dgongs pa rtag tu bskang //
NK010(tha)006:147: dam pa'i chos dang sgrub pa'i gegs gyur pa //
NK010(tha)006:148: mi dang mi min gdug pa gang yang rung //
NK010(tha)006:149: bdag gi zhi dang khro bo'i phrin las kyis //
NK010(tha)006:150: yongs su zhi zhing rnam par gzhom par bgyi //
NK010(tha)006:151: rnal 'byor mchog gi theg chen bla med dang //
NK010(tha)006:152: rdo rje rgyal po khyod la brten nas ni //
NK010(tha)006:153: sangs rgyas zhing sbyong 'gro la sman slad du //
NK010(tha)006:154: byang chub snying po bdag gis rtogs par bgyi //
NK010(tha)006:155: bdag ni 'phags mchog phyag rgya mngon sprul te //
NK010(tha)006:156: gal te skabs med 'chi ba'i dus byung tshe //
NK010(tha)006:157: gsang sngags mgon po ye shes dkyil 'khor can //
NK010(tha)006:158: khyed kyi zhabs kyi drung du mchi bar bgyi //
NK010(tha)006:159: srid gsum sdug bsngal ci 'dra khyed kyis mkhyen //
NK010(tha)006:160: dmyal sogs me dpung zhi bar bgyid la sogs //
NK010(tha)006:161: sems can don la myur du bdag mchi na //
NK010(tha)006:162: dam pa rnams kyis nus mthu stsal du gsol //
NK010(tha)006:163: drug pa byin dbab pa ni /
NK010(tha)006:165: 'phags mchog thugs rje'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)006:166: khyad par bstan pa'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)006:167: mthu rtsal dbyung ba'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)006:168: byin gyis rlob pa'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)006:169: dbang mchog bskur ba'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)006:170: dngos grub stsol ba'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)006:172: byin chen byin phob bcom ldan 'das //
NK010(tha)006:173: dbang chen dbang bskur bcom ldan 'das //
NK010(tha)006:174: dngos grub mchog stsol bcom ldan 'das //
NK010(tha)006:175: bdag cag las 'bras mchis par mdzod //
NK010(tha)006:177: bdun pa mchod rdzas brlab pa la spyi dang bye brag gnyis las /
NK010(tha)006:179: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga d+h+au pe h+aum /
NK010(tha)006:184: g+airti h+r+aih nirti +aah wi ni h+aum /
NK010(tha)006:186: mri tam ge h+r+aih mu rany+dze ah r+au pa h+aum /
NK010(tha)006:188: r+aa sa h+r+aih d+harma d+h+aa tu +aah lan gsum /
NK010(tha)006:190: +aahh+aum sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h+aum h+r+ai th+aah ma
NK010(tha)006:191: h+aa ma lim ta te dz+wa ba lim ta ba
NK010(tha)006:192: la b+aa d+ya gu h+ya sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa
NK010(tha)006:193: / ma h+aa rak+ta dz+wa la man+da la h+aum h+r+ai th+aah lan gsum re bya'o //
NK010(tha)006:194: gnyis pa dngos gzhi la sbyang gzhi ma dag pa snod bcud du 'dzin pa'i snang zhen dang /
NK010(tha)006:195: skye gnas bzhi'i bag chags thabs bskyed pa'i rim pas
NK010(tha)006:196: sbyong bar byed pa la rnam grangs bco lnga las
NK010(tha)006:197: / dang po don dam pa'i byang chub kyi sems
NK010(tha)006:198: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin du ldang ba
NK010(tha)006:200: rdo rje khros pas zhe sdang gcod //
NK010(tha)006:201: mtshon chen sngon po 'bar ba yis //
NK010(tha)006:202: nam mkha'i dkyil nas thig pa shar //
NK010(tha)006:203: srog gi go ru shar ba dang //
NK010(tha)006:204: snying gi go ru bsgom par bya //
NK010(tha)006:205: gnyis pa kun rdzob byang chub kyi sems kun snang du bsgom pa ni /
NK010(tha)006:207: byams dang snying rje dga' ba dang //
NK010(tha)006:208: btang snyoms bzhis bsgral dam tshig ni //
NK010(tha)006:209: bsad cing mnan pa ma yin te //
NK010(tha)006:210: phung po rdo rjes gtams byas nas //
NK010(tha)006:211: rnam par shes pa rdo rjer bsgom //
NK010(tha)006:212: gsum pa rnam shes rdo rjes mtshan nyid rgyu'i ting
NK010(tha)006:213: 'dzin h+aum las rten gzhal yas khang bskyed pa ni
NK010(tha)006:214: / h+aum e yam ra sum kem ram b+h+r+aum /
NK010(tha)006:215: b+h+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he dz+ny+aa na tsakra man+da la b+h+r+aum /
NK010(tha)006:216: srog las nam mkha' gru gsum dang //
NK010(tha)006:217: rlung khrag sha chen keng rus me //
NK010(tha)006:218: 'jigs pa'i dur khrod gzhal yas khang //
NK010(tha)006:219: sgra yi rkyen gyis rab tu rdzogs //
NK010(tha)006:221: mdzes shing 'jigs par rab tu gnas //
NK010(tha)006:222: phyi ni rin chen lnga las grub //
NK010(tha)006:223: dbus su nor bu bee d+aur+ya //
NK010(tha)006:224: shar ni shel yin lho ni gser //
NK010(tha)006:225: nub ni pad+ma r+aa ga la //
NK010(tha)006:226: byang ni in+d+ra n+ai lar gnas //
NK010(tha)006:227: rin chen lnga yi rtsigs pas mdzes //
NK010(tha)006:228: 'dod yon lha mo rin chen brdar //
NK010(tha)006:229: me tog phreng ba mu tig har //
NK010(tha)006:230: t+wa ra na zhing 'khor lo gdugs //
NK010(tha)006:231: ba dan la sogs rab tu mdzes //
NK010(tha)006:232: tog ni rdo rje rtse dgu pa'o //
NK010(tha)006:233: nang ni dur khrod gzhal yas khang //
NK010(tha)006:234: klu chen brgyad kyi ka ba la //
NK010(tha)006:235: nyi ma zla ba lha yi bu //
NK010(tha)006:236: ka gdan ka gzhu mdzes par gnas //
NK010(tha)006:237: lha chen brgyad kyi gdung la ni //
NK010(tha)006:238: zla ba'i skar khung yang dag gnas //
NK010(tha)006:239: gza' chen brgyad kyi lcam la ni //
NK010(tha)006:240: nyi ma'i mthongs khung bcu yis mdzes //
NK010(tha)006:241: nyi shu rtsa brgyad rgyu skar gyi //
NK010(tha)006:242: dral ma rnams su rab tu mdzes //
NK010(tha)006:243: thod pa skam rlon ra ris kyi //
NK010(tha)006:244: phyogs bzhi'i rtsig pa rab tu byas //
NK010(tha)006:245: 'byung po bsnol bas ma them byas //
NK010(tha)006:246: chu srin ya them nyid du byas //
NK010(tha)006:247: ro rlon logs kyi skyes bu la //
NK010(tha)006:248: rigs bzhi klu yi sgo bzhi mdzes //
NK010(tha)006:249: dbus kyi gru gsum mthing nag la //
NK010(tha)006:250: zla gam dmar po gsum dang ldan //
NK010(tha)006:251: 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad nag por gnas //
NK010(tha)006:252: dur khrod brgyad du gnas pa ste //
NK010(tha)006:253: mtsho dang rlung dang sprin dang ni //
NK010(tha)006:254: zhing skyong phyogs skyong mchod rten dang //
NK010(tha)006:255: brag dang me yi rnam par gnas //
NK010(tha)006:256: ro ni rlon pa ra ri dang //
NK010(tha)006:257: keng rus bam rul rnam par 'thor //
NK010(tha)006:258: bya gcan 'jigs pa'i ma mo dang //
NK010(tha)006:259: srid pa'i mkha' 'gro mang po gnas //
NK010(tha)006:260: gzhal yas mdzes shing 'jigs pa der //
NK010(tha)006:261: bzhi pa gdan bskyed pa ni /
NK010(tha)006:262: r+au tra kro d+hi ti ra bam /
NK010(tha)006:266: r+au tra pho mo dam sri bcu //
NK010(tha)006:267: bdud bzhi bgegs bzhi pho mo rnams //
NK010(tha)006:268: kha sbub gan rkyal byi chings mnan //
NK010(tha)006:269: pad+ma nyi zla yon tan spras //
NK010(tha)006:271: lnga pa brten pa'i lha bskyed pa la gsum las /
NK010(tha)006:272: dang po bdag nyid rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa la'ang gnyis kyi /
NK010(tha)006:273: dang po sangs rgyas kyi sras su bdag bya ba ni /
NK010(tha)006:275: rdo rje h+aum yig yongs gyur las //
NK010(tha)006:276: rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum ni //
NK010(tha)006:277: mtshan dang dpe byad yang dag rdzogs //
NK010(tha)006:278: rdo rjee dril bu bde bar 'khyud //
NK010(tha)006:279: kun+da lta bur dkar ba'i mdog /
NK010(tha)006:280: rigs lnga khrag 'thung yab yum bcu //
NK010(tha)006:281: 'dus pa'i rdo rje gzhon nu'i sku //
NK010(tha)006:282: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya d+aip+ta tsakra ha na ha na ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK010(tha)006:283: zhe sdang khrag 'thung rgyal po dang //
NK010(tha)006:284: bde bar sgrol bar byed pa'i yum //
NK010(tha)006:285: khro zhing rngam pa'i tshul bskyed pas //
NK010(tha)006:286: gdug pa ma lus sgrol bar byed //
NK010(tha)006:287: a dang h+aum las rab tu sbyar //
NK010(tha)006:288: yum gyis yab kyi lce gzhibs nas //
NK010(tha)006:289: yum gyi thugs kar ut+pala gtad //
NK010(tha)006:290: gdung ba'i nga ros 'di skad brjod //
NK010(tha)006:292: rdo rje gzhon nu'i rig 'dzin rnams //
NK010(tha)006:293: srid pa rdo rjer grub mdzod cig /
NK010(tha)006:294: srid pa rdo rje phur pa'i lha //
NK010(tha)006:295: ye shes khro bor grub par mdzod //
NK010(tha)006:296: gnyis pa bdag gi sras su sangs rgyas bya ba ni /
NK010(tha)006:297: yab yum sbyor ba mdzad pa las //
NK010(tha)006:298: dgyes mchod gsang ba so sor thob //
NK010(tha)006:299: s+pha ra na phata brjod pa'i //
NK010(tha)006:300: 'od kyis sras bcas rgyal ba mchod //
NK010(tha)006:301: sems can kun gyi sgrib pa sbyangs //
NK010(tha)006:302: sam ha ra na h+aum brjod pas //
NK010(tha)006:303: phyogs bcu'i de bzhin gshegs pa rnams //
NK010(tha)006:304: bkug nas yum gyi mkha' ru bstim //
NK010(tha)006:305: bde chen byang chub sems su gyur //
NK010(tha)006:306: rdo rje dam tshig e ma hoh gnyis med dgyes pa chen po'i ngang //
NK010(tha)006:307: yab yum 'od zhu yi ge h+aum //
NK010(tha)006:308: yongs gyur 'bras bu'i he ru ka /
NK010(tha)006:309: dpal chen rdo rje gzhon nu ni //
NK010(tha)006:310: sgeg pa dpa' ba gar dgu pa //
NK010(tha)006:311: rdzu 'phrul zhabs bzhi dor stabs bgrad //
NK010(tha)006:312: rnam par thar pa'i dbu gsum gyis //
NK010(tha)006:313: skrag mdzad bzhad gshe khro bo'i zhal //
NK010(tha)006:314: g.yas pa ljang nag g.yon dmar nag /
NK010(tha)006:315: spyan dmar smin ma sma ra ser //
NK010(tha)006:316: khro gnyer chu yi rlabs bzhin 'khrug /
NK010(tha)006:317: pha rol phyin drug mtshon pa yi //
NK010(tha)006:318: phyag drug g.yas kyi dang po na //
NK010(tha)006:319: gser gyi rdo rje rtse dgu dang //
NK010(tha)006:320: g.yon gyi dang po me dpung bsnams //
NK010(tha)006:321: g.yas pa rdo rje rtse lnga dang //
NK010(tha)006:322: dgra s+t+wa rdo rje tho ba 'o //
NK010(tha)006:323: kha t+w+aam thod dbyug lcags kyu g.yon //
NK010(tha)006:324: g.yas kyi tha ma phur pa dang //
NK010(tha)006:325: g.yon na phra men rbod gtong ni //
NK010(tha)006:326: khyung dang bya rgod 'ug pa dang //
NK010(tha)006:327: khra dang bya rog pho nyar 'gyed //
NK010(tha)006:328: rdo rje'i gshog pas srid gsum gnon //
NK010(tha)006:329: mthing nag sku la dur khrod chas //
NK010(tha)006:330: rigs lnga thod pa lnga yis brgyan //
NK010(tha)006:331: klu chen brgyad dang thod par brgyan //
NK010(tha)006:333: sbrul dang thod pa gzig gis brgyan //
NK010(tha)006:334: dril bu thod khrag phyag na bsnams //
NK010(tha)006:335: e ka dza ti sgrol ba'i yum //
NK010(tha)006:336: gri gug thod khrag khams gsum sgrol //
NK010(tha)006:337: re 'ga' kha t+w+aam rtse gsum bsnams //
NK010(tha)006:338: g.yer kha dril bu nyid las kyang //
NK010(tha)006:339: rtog med chos kyi sgra 'byin ma //
NK010(tha)006:340: ma mo drug cu pho nyar 'gyed //
NK010(tha)006:341: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya phata dza /
NK010(tha)006:342: ma h+aa bo d+hi tsit+ta man+da la h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)006:343: yab yum 'dod chags nga ro brjod //
NK010(tha)006:344: byin gnyis dam du rab 'khyud de //
NK010(tha)006:345: lag pa dam 'khyud ma mchu gzhibs //
NK010(tha)006:346: rdo rje'i dam tshig glu yi bskul //
NK010(tha)006:348: sangs rgyas kun gyi ye shes sku //
NK010(tha)006:349: ngang nyid rdo rje chos dbyings las //
NK010(tha)006:350: 'bar ba'i khro bo mi bzad pa'i //
NK010(tha)006:351: sku yi dbyig tu sras bskyed cig /
NK010(tha)006:352: gnyis pa phur pa rdzas kyi dkyil 'khor sras kyi rang bzhin du bskyed pa ni /
NK010(tha)006:353: badz+ra bud+d+ha rat+na pad+ma karma k+ai li k+ai la ya h+aum h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)006:354: rdo rje rin chen pad+ma las //
NK010(tha)006:355: de bzhin rigs kyi sras mchog lnga //
NK010(tha)006:356: stod ni gtso bo yab 'dra la //
NK010(tha)006:357: smad ni chu srin phur bu dbal //
NK010(tha)006:359: sku gcig ngang la sku gsum rdzogs //
NK010(tha)006:360: rgya mdud nang nas sngags kyi sgra //
NK010(tha)006:361: 'brug stong lta bur ldir zhing sgrogs //
NK010(tha)006:362: chu srin kha nas me lce 'od //
NK010(tha)006:363: glog ltar 'khyug cing stong gsum gsal //
NK010(tha)006:365: stong gsum gang zhing klu rnams 'dul //
NK010(tha)006:366: thugs ka dpal be'u'i dkyil 'khor na //
NK010(tha)006:367: bzhi bcu rtsa bdun lha tshogs dang //
NK010(tha)006:368: dbu la rigs lnga khrag 'thung rdzogs //
NK010(tha)006:369: dkyil 'khor yongs rdzogs bdag nyid can //
NK010(tha)006:370: dgra s+t+wa g.yas la rang rtags g.yon /
NK010(tha)006:371: bar pa kha t+w+aam gtun shing dang //
NK010(tha)006:372: tha ma ri rab phur bu 'dril //
NK010(tha)006:373: rgyud lnga ye shes lnga ru grol //
NK010(tha)006:374: dug lnga rtsad nas gcod par byed //
NK010(tha)006:375: sangs rgyas 'dus pa thams cad kyi //
NK010(tha)006:376: sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlabs //
NK010(tha)006:377: +aahh+aum k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta badz+ra nan /
NK010(tha)006:378: gsum pa phyogs bcu khro bo'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa ni /
NK010(tha)006:379: gdug pa'i phyogs skyong tshar gcod phyir //
NK010(tha)006:380: yab yum bde ba'i sgo nga bcu //
NK010(tha)006:381: phyung ste phyogs bcur rab tu spro //
NK010(tha)006:382: badz+ra kro d+ha h+aum k+aa ra h+aum /
NK010(tha)006:385: steng phyogs nyi zla'i gdan steng du //
NK010(tha)006:386: khro bo rdo rje h+aum mdzad dang //
NK010(tha)006:387: yum chen rdo rje sgra 'byin ma //
NK010(tha)006:388: sprul pa phag dang rmig bu'i mgo //
NK010(tha)006:389: badz+ra kro d+ha bi dza ya h+aum /
NK010(tha)006:392: shar phyogs dri za'i gdan steng du //
NK010(tha)006:393: khro bo rdo rje rnam par rgyal //
NK010(tha)006:394: yum chen rdo rje snyems ma dang //
NK010(tha)006:395: sprul pa stag dang bya rgod mgo //
NK010(tha)006:396: badz+ra kro d+ha n+ai la dan+da n+ai h+aum /
NK010(tha)006:399: shar lho me lha'i gdan steng du //
NK010(tha)006:400: khro bo rdo rje dbyug sngon can //
NK010(tha)006:401: yum chen rdo rje sder mo dang //
NK010(tha)006:402: sprul pa g.yag dang bya rog mgo //
NK010(tha)006:403: badz+ra kro d+ha ya m+aan+ta ka h+aum /
NK010(tha)006:406: lho phyogs gshin rje'i gdan steng du //
NK010(tha)006:407: khro bo rdo rje gshin rje'i gshed //
NK010(tha)006:408: yum chen dur khrod bdag mo dang //
NK010(tha)006:409: sprul pa sha ba 'ug pa'i mgo //
NK010(tha)006:410: badz+ra kro d+ha +aar+ya a tsa la h+aum /
NK010(tha)006:413: lho nub srin po'i gdan steng du //
NK010(tha)006:414: khro bo chen po mi g.yo mgon //
NK010(tha)006:415: yum chen rdo rje gtun khung ma //
NK010(tha)006:416: sprul pa gzig dang khwa ta'i mgo //
NK010(tha)006:417: badz+ra kro d+ha h+ya g+r+ai wa h+r+aih hu lu h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)006:419: nub phyogs klu dbang gdan steng du //
NK010(tha)006:420: khro bo chen po rta mgrin rgyal //
NK010(tha)006:421: yum chen rdo rje gtum mo dang //
NK010(tha)006:422: sprul pa byi la pu shud mgo //
NK010(tha)006:423: badz+ra kro d+ha a pa ra tsit+ta h+aum /
NK010(tha)006:426: nub byang rlung lha'i gdan steng du //
NK010(tha)006:427: khro bo chen po gzhan mi thub //
NK010(tha)006:428: yum chen rdo rje mda' snyems ma //
NK010(tha)006:429: sprul pa spyang ki khra yi mgo //
NK010(tha)006:430: badz+ra kro d+ha a mri ta kun+da li h+aum /
NK010(tha)006:433: byang phyogs gnod sbyin gdan steng du //
NK010(tha)006:434: khro bo rdo rje bdud rtsi 'khyil //
NK010(tha)006:435: yum chen rdo rje rlung 'byin ma //
NK010(tha)006:436: sprul pa seng ge pha wang mgo //
NK010(tha)006:437: badz+ra kro d+ha tree lokya bi dza ya h+aum /
NK010(tha)006:440: byang shar 'byung po'i gdan steng du //
NK010(tha)006:441: khro bo rdo rje khams gsum rgyal //
NK010(tha)006:442: yum chen rdo rje gsod ma dang //
NK010(tha)006:443: sprul pa dom dang sre mong mgo //
NK010(tha)006:444: badz+ra kro d+ha ma h+aa ba la h+aum /
NK010(tha)006:447: 'og phyogs sa bdag gdan steng du //
NK010(tha)006:448: khro bo rdo rje stobs po che //
NK010(tha)006:449: yum chen rdo rje bskyod ma dang //
NK010(tha)006:450: sprul pa dred dang byi ba'i mgo //
NK010(tha)006:451: lha ni bzhi bcu 'di rnams kyang //
NK010(tha)006:452: zhal gcig phyag gnyis mdog nag gzugs //
NK010(tha)006:453: stag dang gzig gi sham thabs can //
NK010(tha)006:454: mche ba can dang gshog pa can //
NK010(tha)006:455: phra men mgo brnyan nyi shu ni //
NK010(tha)006:456: sbrul dang thod pas rab tu brgyan //
NK010(tha)006:457: phur pa lcags kyu phyag na bsnams //
NK010(tha)006:458: skra bardzesa spyan dmar mche ba gtsigs //
NK010(tha)006:460: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya bi da ya bi da ya h+aum phata //
NK010(tha)006:461: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya na mahs man+ta hrim hrim h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)006:462: badz+ra k+ai li l+ai la ya pra su ru pra su ru h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)006:463: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya m+aa ra ya m+aa ra ya h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)006:464: nyi zla yi ge bzhi nyid las //
NK010(tha)006:465: drod gsher las skyes sgo ma bzhi //
NK010(tha)006:466: shar phyogs dri za'i gdan steng du //
NK010(tha)006:467: skye ka'i mgo can lcags kyu ma //
NK010(tha)006:468: lho phyogs grul bum gdan steng du //
NK010(tha)006:469: pu shud mgo can zhags pa ma //
NK010(tha)006:470: nub phyogs chu bdag gdan steng du //
NK010(tha)006:471: srin bya'i mgo can lcags sgrog ma //
NK010(tha)006:472: byang phyogs gnod sbyin gdan steng du //
NK010(tha)006:473: khra yi mgo can dril bu ma //
NK010(tha)006:474: 'di bzhi zhal gcig phyag gnyis ma //
NK010(tha)006:475: dkar ser dmar dang ljang ba'i mdog /
NK010(tha)006:476: gzig dang thod sbrul rgyan du byas //
NK010(tha)006:477: bskum zhing brkyang ba'i stabs kyis mnan //
NK010(tha)006:478: phyag g.yon phur pa 'debs par mdzad //
NK010(tha)006:479: me dpung dkyil na khro tshul bzhugs //
NK010(tha)006:480: lha ni brgyad dang bzhi bcu rnams //
NK010(tha)006:481: drag po'i tshul gyis zhe sdang 'joms //
NK010(tha)006:482: mu ran la ni phur srung ste //
NK010(tha)006:483: e yam ma ya bzhi nyid las //
NK010(tha)006:484: shwa na mu kha bzhi po gsal //
NK010(tha)006:485: dzahyiga bzhi las sa bdag bzhi //
NK010(tha)006:486: b+h+yo yig bzhi las bdag nyid bzhi //
NK010(tha)006:487: mthu dang rdzu 'phrul glog las myur //
NK010(tha)006:488: bstan pa bsrung zhing nyams pa bdun //
NK010(tha)006:489: zhe la gnag pa'i stobs kyis sgrol //
NK010(tha)006:491: dpal chen dkyil 'khor gcig tu rdzogs //
NK010(tha)006:492: bzhi pa byin gyis rlob pa ni /
NK010(tha)006:493: snying ga mgrin pa spyi bo ru //
NK010(tha)006:494: zla ba'i dkyil 'khor bsam nas ni //
NK010(tha)006:497: thugs kyi rdo rje la sogs bsgom //
NK010(tha)006:498: de nyid shes rab sku rgyas ma //
NK010(tha)006:499: lha mo rnams kyi 'od tshogs kyis //
NK010(tha)006:500: dus gsum phyogs rnams khyab pa yis //
NK010(tha)006:501: ma lus sangs rgyas drangs mchod nas //
NK010(tha)006:502: bkra shis don byed rnams la ni //
NK010(tha)006:503: rang gi thugs srog rdo rje yis //
NK010(tha)006:504: de la byin rlabs bskul bar bya //
NK010(tha)006:505: rang sngags dang bstun rdo rje rtse lnga pa'i phyag rgya gnas so sor gtug cing /
NK010(tha)006:507: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK010(tha)006:511: lnga pa dbang bskur ba la gsum las /
NK010(tha)006:512: dkyil 'khor gsum gyi srog ye shes su dbang bskur ba ni /
NK010(tha)006:513: snying gar b+h+r+aum las rin po che'i gzhal med khang
NK010(tha)006:514: sgo gcig pa'i sgo srung rta mgrin yab yum du
NK010(tha)006:515: gnas pa'i nang du h+aum las ye shes sems dpa'
NK010(tha)006:516: tshon gang ba gcig bsam la /
NK010(tha)006:517: ye shes dpa' bo'i thugs ka yi //
NK010(tha)006:518: 'od kyis mgon po rnams bskul nas //
NK010(tha)006:519: de dag thugs las byung ba yi //
NK010(tha)006:520: rig mas bdud rtsi bum chu yis //
NK010(tha)006:521: dbang bskur byas te thim gyur nas //
NK010(tha)006:522: rang sngags rdo rje can gyi gzung //
NK010(tha)006:523: dbu rgyan rnams la rigs lnga dang //
NK010(tha)006:524: rigs kyi bdag po rnams kyis rgyan //
NK010(tha)006:525: ye shes sems dpa'i thugs ka'i 'od kyis phyogs bcu'i
NK010(tha)006:526: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs brgyud bskul
NK010(tha)006:527: bas de rnams kyi thugs ka nas byung ba'i rdo
NK010(tha)006:528: rje btsun mo'i b+ha ga la gdan gsum tshang ba'i
NK010(tha)006:529: dkyil 'khor rdzogs pa mdun gyi nam mkha' la byon
NK010(tha)006:530: / sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa a nu
NK010(tha)006:531: r+aa ga dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a
NK010(tha)006:532: / ham / zhes bskul bas lha tshogs rnams bde stong gi ros tshim /
NK010(tha)006:533: rjes chags kyi mes 'od du zhu ba'i bdud rtsi bum pa'i chus mgo bo'i gnas lngar dbang bskur /
NK010(tha)006:534: nyon mongs pa lnga'i dri ma sbyangs /
NK010(tha)006:535: phung po lnga rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas su gnas gyur
NK010(tha)006:536: pa nas bzung ste khams dang skye mched thams cad
NK010(tha)006:537: lha'i rang bzhin du rnam par dag /
NK010(tha)006:538: dbang bzhi'i dam tshig las byung ba'i dga' ba bzhi'i ye shes nyams su myong /
NK010(tha)006:539: chu lhag ma spyi bor brtan pa yongs su gyur
NK010(tha)006:540: pa las rdo rje mi bskyod pa dbus su bzhugs
NK010(tha)006:541: pa'i rigs lngas dbu brgyan par gyur par bsam la
NK010(tha)006:542: / dang po rjes su bskul ba ni /
NK010(tha)006:544: thabs kyi spyod pas 'gro don du //
NK010(tha)006:545: byams dang snying rjes gang 'dul ba //
NK010(tha)006:546: sangs rgyas phrin las rdzogs mdzad pa //
NK010(tha)006:547: dbang dang byin rlabs bdag stsol cig /
NK010(tha)006:548: rdo rje phyi bsdams las gung mo brkyang ba mi bskyod pa'i dbang rgya spyi bor bzhag la /
NK010(tha)006:549: ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK010(tha)006:550: de las mdzub mo gnyis brkyang ba rnam snang gi dbang rgya dpral bar bzhag la /
NK010(tha)006:551: ma h+aa +aa dar+sha dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK010(tha)006:552: srin lag brkyang pa rin 'byung gi dbang rgya rna ltag g.yas su bzhag la /
NK010(tha)006:553: ma h+aa sa ma t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK010(tha)006:554: mthe bong brkyang ba snang mtha'i dbang rgya ltag par bzhag la /
NK010(tha)006:555: ma h+aa pra t+ya bek+sha na dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK010(tha)006:556: mathe'u chung brkyang pa don grub kyi dbang rgya rna ltag g.yon par bzhag la /
NK010(tha)006:557: ma h+aa kri ta a nush+tha dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK010(tha)006:558: gnyis pa dkyil 'khor gsum gyis khams gsum gyi srog la dbang bskur ba ni /
NK010(tha)006:560: 'gro drug nyon mongs bcings pa rnams //
NK010(tha)006:561: h+aum gis dug chen rab sbyangs te //
NK010(tha)006:562: a n+ri su tri pre dur gyur //
NK010(tha)006:563: ram yam kham las me rlung chus //
NK010(tha)006:564: 'gro ba rab sbyangs h+aum du gyur //
NK010(tha)006:565: khams gsum thams cad rdo rje sems //
NK010(tha)006:566: til gyi gang bu lta bus gang //
NK010(tha)006:567: gsum pa ye shes sems dpa'i srog la lhan cig
NK010(tha)006:568: skyes pa'i ye shes chen po'i dbang bskur ba ni
NK010(tha)006:570: rta mgrin rgyal po ye shes la //
NK010(tha)006:571: bstim pas byang chub sems rgyas gyur //
NK010(tha)006:572: yab yum gnyis med sbyor ba'i sgras //
NK010(tha)006:573: ye shes khro bo spyan drang ngo //
NK010(tha)006:574: drug pa spyan drang ba ni /
NK010(tha)006:575: spos rol gdung ba'i dbyangs dang bcas /
NK010(tha)006:577: rdo rje gzhon nu'i dam tshig gis //
NK010(tha)006:578: srid pa phur bur bsgrub pa dang //
NK010(tha)006:579: dbang dang dngos grub stsol ba'i phyir //
NK010(tha)006:580: ma bcos thig le'i chos nyid las //
NK010(tha)006:581: 'gyur med sku gcig gnas pa de //
NK010(tha)006:582: ye shes khro bo chen po yin //
NK010(tha)006:583: khro bo chen po gshegs nas kyang //
NK010(tha)006:584: rtags dang mtshan ma ston pa dang //
NK010(tha)006:585: rdo rje phur pa'i dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)006:586: sras mchog rigs lnga'i dam tshig gis //
NK010(tha)006:587: srid pa phur bur bsgrub pa dang //
NK010(tha)006:588: dbang dang dngos grub stsol ba'i phyir //

NK010(tha)006:590: ye shes khro bo gshegs nas kyang //
NK010(tha)006:591: rtags dang mtshan ma ston pa dang //
NK010(tha)006:592: rdo rje phur pa'i dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)006:593: phyogs bcu khro bo'i dam tshig gis //
NK010(tha)006:594: srid pa phur bur bsgrub pa dang //
NK010(tha)006:595: dbang dang dngos grub stsol ba'i phyir //
NK010(tha)006:596: ye shes khro bo gshegs su gsol //
NK010(tha)006:597: khro bo chen po gshegs nas kyang //
NK010(tha)006:598: rtags dang mtshan ma ston pa dang //
NK010(tha)006:599: rdo rje phur pa'i dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)006:600: e h+ye hi b+ha ga w+aa na /
NK010(tha)006:601: ma h+aa ka ru ni ka dri sh+ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK010(tha)006:602: sa ma ya hoh e a ra li ho /
NK010(tha)006:603: bdun pa rig pa'i me tog dor ba ni /
NK010(tha)006:605: +aahbadz+ra sa ma ya +aah h+aum badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum /
NK010(tha)006:606: s+w+aa badz+ra sa ma ya s+w+aa /
NK010(tha)006:607: h+aa badz+ra sa ma ya h+aa /
NK010(tha)006:609: ye shes rgyal po sku gsung thugs //
NK010(tha)006:610: yon tan phrin las rmad po che //
NK010(tha)006:611: de nyid du ni mnyam sbyor ba'i //
NK010(tha)006:612: phyag rgya chen por bdag sbyor cig /
NK010(tha)006:613: dzahh+aum bam hoh h+aum ha he phata /
NK010(tha)006:616: thugs mchog gsal ba'i byin rlabs las //
NK010(tha)006:617: zhe sdang gnas su 'joms pa dang //
NK010(tha)006:618: me long ye shes 'thob bya'i phyir //
NK010(tha)006:619: dkyil 'khor dbus su bzhugs su gsol //
NK010(tha)006:620: dkyil 'khor dbus su bzhugs nas kyang //
NK010(tha)006:621: nyon mongs mun pa bsal du gsol //

NK010(tha)006:623: dur khrod chen po'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK010(tha)006:624: zhing bcu bsgral ba'i gdan steng du //
NK010(tha)006:625: dgyes shing brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK010(tha)006:626: dgyes shing brtan par bzhugs nas kyang //

NK010(tha)006:628: phyogs bcu dur khrod gzhal yas su //
NK010(tha)006:629: khro rgyal sprul par bcas pa yang //
NK010(tha)006:630: phyogs skyong bsnol ba'i gdan steng du //
NK010(tha)006:631: dgyes shing brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK010(tha)006:632: dgyes shing brtan par bzhugs nas kyang //

NK010(tha)006:637: yang dag don la sku ni cir snang yang //

NK010(tha)006:639: 'dul ba'i dbang du rab rngams mche ba gtsigs //
NK010(tha)006:640: h+aum dang phata kyi sgras ni kun kyang bkang //
NK010(tha)006:641: nyon mongs gdug pa 'dul ba'i thugs rje yis //
NK010(tha)006:642: byin rlabs ster ba'i lha la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK010(tha)006:643: a ti pu hoh pra t+aits+tsha hoh bcu pa mchod pa la brgyad las /
NK010(tha)006:646: bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK010(tha)006:647: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i ye shes kyi //
NK010(tha)006:648: srid pa rgya mtsho mtha' yas kun //
NK010(tha)006:649: kun bzang mchod sprin mchog tu rol //
NK010(tha)006:653: sku la dag bya mi mnga' yang //
NK010(tha)006:654: sems can rnams la bsod nams phyir //
NK010(tha)006:655: phyag zhabs nye reg mdzad nas kyang //
NK010(tha)006:656: rdo rje'i gdan la tish+tha lhan /
NK010(tha)006:657: +aa ha ra +aa ha ra sarba bid+y+aa d+ha ra
NK010(tha)006:658: p+au dzi te na mahs man+ta bud+d+h+aa n+aam ga ga
NK010(tha)006:659: na kham sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK010(tha)006:660: gsum pa lha mo bcu drug ni /
NK010(tha)006:662: snying rje'i sgeg mo blta na sdug /
NK010(tha)006:663: byams pa'i phreng ldan 'gro la brtse //
NK010(tha)006:664: dga' ba'i glu mkhan gzhan yid 'phrog /
NK010(tha)006:665: kun la btang snyoms gar ma yis //
NK010(tha)006:666: dkyil 'khor dgyes pa bskyed gyur cig /
NK010(tha)006:667: so so'i phyag rgya dang bcas /
NK010(tha)006:670: badz+ra g+airti h+r+aih badz+ra n+airti a /
NK010(tha)006:671: tshul khrims spos ldan yid du 'ong //
NK010(tha)006:672: bzod pa'i me tog blta na mdzes //
NK010(tha)006:673: bsam gtan sgron me bzhin bzang ma //
NK010(tha)006:674: shes rab dri ldan byug pa mos //
NK010(tha)006:675: dkyil 'khor dgyes pa bskyed gyur cig /
NK010(tha)006:678: badz+ra +aa lo ke h+r+aih badz+ra gan+d+he +aa /
NK010(tha)006:679: sbyin lag yangs pa'i pi wang sgreng //
NK010(tha)006:680: brtson 'grus gling bus gzhan snang bsgyur //
NK010(tha)006:681: smon pa'i rnga zlum bzhin ras mdzes //
NK010(tha)006:682: 'jug pa'i rdza rnga kun tu rgyus //
NK010(tha)006:683: dkyil 'khor dgyes pa bskyed gyur cig /
NK010(tha)006:686: badz+ra mri tam ge h+r+aih badz+ra mu rany+dze a /
NK010(tha)006:687: gtong la goms pa gzugs ma'o //
NK010(tha)006:688: snyan par smra ba reg pa sprod //
NK010(tha)006:689: don spyod ro brgya'i dpal 'dzin can //
NK010(tha)006:690: don mthun chos kyi 'byung gnas mas //
NK010(tha)006:691: dkyil 'khor dgyes pa bskyed gyur cig /
NK010(tha)006:694: badz+ra ra sa h+r+aih badz+ra d+harma d+h+aa tu a /
NK010(tha)006:697: sangs rgyas kun dang mnyam sbyor zhing //
NK010(tha)006:698: rang byung gdod nas rnam par dag /
NK010(tha)006:699: rtsa brgyad yan lag stong sbyar sman //
NK010(tha)006:700: rigs lnga dam tshig lnga yi dngos //
NK010(tha)006:701: sgron ma lnga dang bdud rtsi lnga //
NK010(tha)006:702: rgyud lnga dug lnga 'joms pa'i bdud //
NK010(tha)006:703: ye shes lnga po grub pa'i rtsi //
NK010(tha)006:704: 'chi ba med pa'i dam rdzas che //
NK010(tha)006:706: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK010(tha)006:709: he ru ka yi gnas bcu dang //
NK010(tha)006:710: dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad nas //
NK010(tha)006:711: dpal chen 'khor bcas spyan drangs te //
NK010(tha)006:712: dur khrod mchog gi gnas 'di ru //
NK010(tha)006:713: zhing chen gsar rnying ti rar bcas //
NK010(tha)006:714: dmar gyi ar+g+ham rgya mtshor bskyil //
NK010(tha)006:716: ma lus gshegs nas bsnams su gsol //
NK010(tha)006:717: ma h+aa ba lim ta kh+aa hi /
NK010(tha)006:718: drug pa rak+ta tshar gsum ni /
NK010(tha)006:720: dang po pho nya la bka' bsgo ba'i phyir phul nas /
NK010(tha)006:722: dngos grub bar chad byed pa'i gegs //
NK010(tha)006:723: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NK010(tha)006:724: zung zhig rgyob cig rnam par chings //
NK010(tha)006:725: gtogs shig srog dang bral bar gyis //
NK010(tha)006:726: rengs par khug la smrar chug cig /
NK010(tha)006:727: phob cig rnam par gzir bar gyis //
NK010(tha)006:728: nga yi dbang du gyur nas kyang //
NK010(tha)006:729: bsgo ba'i bka' 'di nyan par byos //
NK010(tha)006:731: gnyis pa dam can gnad la dbab pa'i phyir dbul ba ni /
NK010(tha)006:733: bran dang bka' nyan pho nya'i tshogs //
NK010(tha)006:734: khyed kyi dam tshig dus la bab //
NK010(tha)006:735: sngon chad ji bzhin bcas pa yis //
NK010(tha)006:736: mngon spyod phrin las myur du mdzod //
NK010(tha)006:738: gsum pa mthu dang rdzu 'phrul 'phrog pa'i ched du 'bul ba ni /
NK010(tha)006:740: dngos grub bar chad byed pa'i gegs //
NK010(tha)006:741: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NK010(tha)006:743: nga la bar chad byed pa rnams //
NK010(tha)006:744: mthu dang rdzu 'phrul med par mdzod //
NK010(tha)006:746: bdun pa sbyor sgrol gyi mchod pa ni /
NK010(tha)006:748: lag pa khrag 'thung yab yum bcus //
NK010(tha)006:749: dug gsum rtsad nas gcad pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)006:750: khams gsum yongs sgrol sbyor ba byas //
NK010(tha)006:752: rdungs shig rdo rje 'bar ba'i gtun //
NK010(tha)006:753: bka' las 'da' byed sdig can rnams //
NK010(tha)006:754: rdo rje me dbal snying bsregs nas //
NK010(tha)006:755: lus ngag rdul phran bzhin du rlog /
NK010(tha)006:756: khro mo 'bar ba'i gtun khung du //
NK010(tha)006:757: rdo rje tho bas brdung byas nas //
NK010(tha)006:758: lha yang rung ste bsgral bar gyis //
NK010(tha)006:759: kha tham kha tham kha tham /
NK010(tha)006:760: kh+aa hi kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK010(tha)006:764: brgyad pa don dam gyi mchod pa ni /
NK010(tha)006:766: yang dag don gyi phur pa ni //
NK010(tha)006:767: ma spangs ma bsgrubs btsal du med //
NK010(tha)006:768: ma bslad ma bcos bsgyur du med //
NK010(tha)006:769: lta ba don dam rtogs pa la //
NK010(tha)006:770: rol pa cir yang 'gag pa med //
NK010(tha)006:771: de nyid rtogs na phur pa'i don //
NK010(tha)006:772: don dam rtogs pas thugs dam bskang //
NK010(tha)006:773: bsnyen pa'i tshe de tsam ma nus na mchod pa thams cad /
NK010(tha)006:774: bla med mchog gi mchod pa dam pa ni //
NK010(tha)006:776: bcu gcig pa bstod pa ni /
NK010(tha)006:778: sgeg pa dpal ba 'jigs su rung ba dang //
NK010(tha)006:779: dgod dang gshe dang 'jigs par byed pa dang //
NK010(tha)006:780: snying rje rngam zhi rdo rje gzhon nu'i sku //
NK010(tha)006:781: zhe sdang 'joms pa'i lha la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK010(tha)006:782: yab kyi thugs dam dgyes pa skong ba'i yum //
NK010(tha)006:784: e ka dza ti zhe sdang 'joms mdzad ma //
NK010(tha)006:785: 'dod chags tshul gyis 'dod chags 'joms la bstod //
NK010(tha)006:786: ye shes lnga ldan phur bus dug lnga 'joms //
NK010(tha)006:787: phrin las lnga yi dregs pa sgrol ba la //
NK010(tha)006:788: thogs pa med pa'i las mdzad 'dus pa lnga //
NK010(tha)006:789: sras mchog rigs lnga'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK010(tha)006:790: ye shes rol pa'i stobs bcus mi dge 'joms //
NK010(tha)006:791: sku gsung thugs kyis gdug pa sgrol bar mdzad //
NK010(tha)006:792: yang dag don gyis log 'dren 'joms mdzad pa //
NK010(tha)006:793: khro bo yab yum bcu la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK010(tha)006:794: byang chub bde la sgrol ba'i pho nya mo //
NK010(tha)006:795: ye shes don la khra thabs gzugs 'dzin cing //
NK010(tha)006:796: dregs pa'i tshogs rnams ma lus 'dul mdzad pa //
NK010(tha)006:797: phra men pho nya'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK010(tha)006:798: bcu gnyis pa dam bca' ba ni /
NK010(tha)006:799: bskal pa dpag tu med pa tshun chod nas //
NK010(tha)006:800: da lta'i lus 'di bskyed pa phan chod du //
NK010(tha)006:801: lha mchog khyed dang smon lam mthun bsdebs nas //
NK010(tha)006:802: dus 'dir zhal mthong yi dam lhar gsol na //
NK010(tha)006:803: dus tshig 'di nas bzung nas yi dam lha //
NK010(tha)006:804: snying po byang chub mchog la mi gnas tshun //
NK010(tha)006:805: tshe rabs 'khor ba gar byung gar skyes kyang //
NK010(tha)006:806: gsang ba'i lha mchog khyod dang mi 'bral zhing //
NK010(tha)006:807: spyi dang khyad par lhag pa'i dam tshig las //
NK010(tha)006:808: mi 'da' ba dang yun du bdag srung gis //
NK010(tha)006:809: chad lhag 'gal 'khrul mchis na mthol lo bshags //
NK010(tha)006:810: bar chad rkyen gyi rnam smin ci byung yang //
NK010(tha)006:811: dpal chen khyed kyis mod la zil gyis gnon //
NK010(tha)006:812: dngos grub mchog stsol shes rab lha mo'i tshogs //
NK010(tha)006:815: thugs kar dpal gyi be'u'i dkyil 'khor ni //
NK010(tha)006:816: sgo gcig rin chen gzhal yas khang //
NK010(tha)006:817: bde stong dbyer med ngang nyid las //
NK010(tha)006:818: chos kyi sku las longs skur shar //
NK010(tha)006:819: pad+ma zla ba'i gdan la bzhugs //
NK010(tha)006:820: skyon gyis ma gos gti mug sel //
NK010(tha)006:821: yab yum gnyis med zag med sku //
NK010(tha)006:822: sku mdog dkar gsal rnam dag dbyings //
NK010(tha)006:823: rdo rje dril bu phyag na bsnams //
NK010(tha)006:824: shes rab byang chub sems dang ldan //
NK010(tha)006:825: rtog med mi 'gyur skyil krung bzhugs //
NK010(tha)006:826: mkha' dbyings bde chen sku la bstod //
NK010(tha)006:828: bcu bzhi pa bzlas pa la bsnyen pa dang /
NK010(tha)006:831: sgrub pa chen po dang bzhi las /
NK010(tha)006:833: gtso bo'i thugs kar ye shes sems dpa' zhi ba
NK010(tha)006:834: longs spyod rdzogs sku yum dang bcas pa'i thugs kar
NK010(tha)006:835: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs rdo rje'i
NK010(tha)006:836: ngo bo rdo rje mthing nag rtse lnga dang /
NK010(tha)006:837: de'i lte bar nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng ting 'dzin sems dpa' h+aum mthing nag la /
NK010(tha)006:838: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h+aum /
NK010(tha)006:839: zhes pa'i sngags phreng mthing nag spus bris pa lta
NK010(tha)006:840: bur 'khor bar dmigs la chos nyid don dang ma
NK010(tha)006:841: bral ba'i yongs grub kyi lhar snang dang nga rgyal
NK010(tha)006:842: la re mos su slob pa ste /
NK010(tha)006:844: lha yi nga rgyal rab gnas pa //
NK010(tha)006:845: brjed pa med pa'i dran pa ni //
NK010(tha)006:846: 'bad pa med pa'i tshogs chen po //
NK010(tha)006:847: mkhas pas rtag tu bsam par bya //
NK010(tha)006:849: de lta bu'i lhar snang la gsal brtan cung zad thob nas 'od zer spro bsdu ni /
NK010(tha)006:850: thugs srog ting 'dzin sems dpa' las 'od zer bung
NK010(tha)006:851: ba'i mtshon cha lta bu 'phros pas sangs rgyas kyi
NK010(tha)006:852: zhing khams thams cad g.yos shing mnyes pa'i mchod pa
NK010(tha)006:853: phul / sems can gyi khams la 'phros pas sdig sgrib sbyangs /
NK010(tha)006:854: dag pa'i snod bcud 'ba' zhig tu gyur pas don gnyis byas /
NK010(tha)006:855: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs
NK010(tha)006:856: kyi byin rlabs sku dang yig 'bru phyag mtshan gyi
NK010(tha)006:857: rnam par byung ste rang nyid la thim pas rgyud
NK010(tha)006:858: byin gyis brlabs shing dngos grub thob par bsam mo
NK010(tha)006:859: // bsnyen tshad ni las rung tsam la 'bum phrag bcu tham pa'o //
NK010(tha)006:861: bsnyen pa'i sngags de nyid la /
NK010(tha)006:862: sarba big nan bam h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)006:863: btags pa'i yig 'bru bcu bzhi pa ste /
NK010(tha)006:864: sgrub thabs dpag bsam ljon pa ltar dzapa khang dbye
NK010(tha)006:865: nas bdag mdun tha dad du byas te do li
NK010(tha)006:866: la gtso bor bslab par bya ste /
NK010(tha)006:868: sngags phreng las rang 'dra gnyis pa re chad pa lu gu rgyud du 'brel /
NK010(tha)006:869: rdo rje'i dbus rwa nas 'thon ye shes sems dpa'i sku'i dbyibs brgyud zhal du 'thon /
NK010(tha)006:870: rim bzhin bdag nyid rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi shangs bug g.yas pa las 'thon /
NK010(tha)006:871: rdo rje gzhon nu ye shes pa'i shangs bug g.yon nas zhugs te thugs kar thim /
NK010(tha)006:872: sku gsung thugs mnyes pa'i mchod pa phul /
NK010(tha)006:874: de'i shangs bug g.yas nas brgyud rang gi sna bug g.yon du zhugs /
NK010(tha)006:875: rim par brgyud pas bdag mdun gyi rten dang brten pa thams cad shin tu gsal bar byas /
NK010(tha)006:878: dngos grub rnam pa gnyis bde blag tu thob par bsam mo //
NK010(tha)006:879: bsnyen tshad ni 'bum phrag bcu drug go //
NK010(tha)006:881: yig 'bru bcu bzhi pa nyid la /
NK010(tha)006:883: gsum bsnan pa'i bcu bdun pa ste 'bum phrag gcig
NK010(tha)006:884: la sogs ji ltar rigs pa'i grangs dus mtshan ma'i
NK010(tha)006:885: bsnyen sgrub tshad du phyin par bya'o //
NK010(tha)006:886: bzhi pa sgrub pa chen po ni /
NK010(tha)006:887: skabs 'dir smad las kyi ngo bo dam can nye
NK010(tha)006:888: bar bsnyen pa la bya ste gzhan du shes par
NK010(tha)006:889: bya'o // bco lnga pa 'dzab mjug bsdu ba ni /
NK010(tha)006:890: mchod bstod kyi mthar yi ge brgya pa lan gsum gyis nongs bshags mthar /
NK010(tha)006:891: bskyed rim gyis rtag mtha' bsal ba'i nyer bsdu dang /
NK010(tha)006:892: chad mtha' bsam phyir gnyug ma'i he ru kar ldang ba yang shes par bya'o //
NK010(tha)006:893: spyi don gsum pa rjes kyi rim pa la bcu drug las /
NK010(tha)006:894: dang po tshogs byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK010(tha)006:896: dpa' chen thugs las ram yam kham //
NK010(tha)006:898: snang srid bde chen ka p+aa lar //
NK010(tha)006:899: bcud rnams rigs lnga'i dam rdzas gyur //
NK010(tha)006:900: +aahh+aum ha ho h+r+aih gnyis pa tshogs zhing spyan 'dren pa ni /
NK010(tha)006:902: 'og min chos dbyings pho brang dang //
NK010(tha)006:903: yan lag bdun ldan longs spyod rdzogs //
NK010(tha)006:904: rang bzhin sprul sku'i zhing khams nas //
NK010(tha)006:905: dpal chen dkyil 'khor lha tshogs dang //
NK010(tha)006:906: gnas dang nye gnas rnam pa gnyis //
NK010(tha)006:907: yul ni rol pa nye yul rol //
NK010(tha)006:908: zhing dang nye ba'i zhing dang ni //
NK010(tha)006:910: tshan d+ho nye ba'i tshan d+ho ste //
NK010(tha)006:911: he ru ka yi gnas bcu dang //
NK010(tha)006:912: dur khrod chen po bsil ba'i tshal //
NK010(tha)006:913: oo di ya nar pad+ma brtsegs //
NK010(tha)006:914: za hor yul na khu byug klong //
NK010(tha)006:915: sing nga'i yul na sku la rdzogs //
NK010(tha)006:916: kha che'i yul na he chen rol //
NK010(tha)006:917: bal po'i yul na ya ma kha //
NK010(tha)006:918: tho gar yul na gsang chen rol //
NK010(tha)006:919: li yul 'jig rten mngon rdzogs te //
NK010(tha)006:920: dur khrod chen po brgyad rnams na //
NK010(tha)006:921: bzhugs pa'i dpa' bo mkha' 'gro dang //
NK010(tha)006:923: tshogs la spyan 'dren gshegs su gsol //
NK010(tha)006:924: tshogs khang 'di ni sprul pa'i zhing //
NK010(tha)006:925: tshogs rdzas 'dod yon rol pa'i rgyan //
NK010(tha)006:926: thabs dang shes rab lcam dral ldan //
NK010(tha)006:927: rdo rje glu gar byin re chags //
NK010(tha)006:928: cang te'u dril bu snyan cing 'khrol //
NK010(tha)006:929: 'di ni dam tshig mchog gi gnas //
NK010(tha)006:930: shags dang rtsod pa ku co med //
NK010(tha)006:931: rig pa brtul zhugs nyams dang ldan //
NK010(tha)006:932: dam tshig 'di ni dang du bzhes //
NK010(tha)006:933: mchog dang thun mong dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)006:934: gu ru d+he wa d+aa ka d+aa ki ni d+harma
NK010(tha)006:935: p+aa la sa ma ya dzah gsum pa tshogs phud
NK010(tha)006:937: sangs rgyas dam tshig bla na med //
NK010(tha)006:938: sha lnga bdud rtsi rnam pa lnga //
NK010(tha)006:939: bza' bca' btung ba phyi yi tshogs //
NK010(tha)006:940: 'dod yon lha mo rnam pa lnga //
NK010(tha)006:941: dbang po'i longs spyod nang gi tshogs //
NK010(tha)006:942: bde stong ye shes bla na med //
NK010(tha)006:943: dga' bzhi rnam rol gsang ba'i tshogs //
NK010(tha)006:945: bzhes nas dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)006:946: ga na tsa kra p+au dza ho /
NK010(tha)006:947: bzhi pa bar du bshags pa ni /
NK010(tha)006:949: gang zhig 'khrul par gyur pa de nas bzung //
NK010(tha)006:950: rnam smin lus la brten pa de srid du //
NK010(tha)006:951: mi dge bcu dang mtshams med nye ba lnga //
NK010(tha)006:952: lci ba bcu drug log pa brgyad la sogs //
NK010(tha)006:953: theg pa gsum dang rig pa 'dzin pa yi //
NK010(tha)006:954: sdom gsum dam tshig nyams pa mtha' dag kun //
NK010(tha)006:955: ga na tshogs kyi 'khor lo la brten nas //
NK010(tha)006:956: 'chab pa med pa'i sems kyis mthol lo bshags //
NK010(tha)006:957: dag tshangs chen po'i dngos grub bdag la stsol //
NK010(tha)006:958: he ru ka'i yig brgya brjod /
NK010(tha)006:959: lnga pa tha ma bsgral mchod ni /
NK010(tha)006:960: e las thar med srid brub khung nang //
NK010(tha)006:961: ma rig 'khrul pas bcings pa bdag lta'i dgra //
NK010(tha)006:962: ye shes dbyings la sgrib pa'i gzung 'dzin bgegs //
NK010(tha)006:963: dag chen ye shes rig pa'i lcags kyus zungs //
NK010(tha)006:964: mnyam par ma bzhag med pa'i zhags pas chings //
NK010(tha)006:965: lhag mthong lu gu rgyud kyi d+r+wa bas sdoms //
NK010(tha)006:966: rjes thob 'khrul pa med pa'i dril bus myos //
NK010(tha)006:967: phung po lnga yi nye bar len pa kun //
NK010(tha)006:968: bdag med rtogs pa'i mtshon gyis rnam par gtubs //
NK010(tha)006:969: skye med khros pa'i lha tshogs zhal du bstab //
NK010(tha)006:970: m+aam sa rak+ta tsit+ta go ro tsa na ba su
NK010(tha)006:971: ta kem ni ri ti ta na tsakra p+au tsa
NK010(tha)006:972: kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK010(tha)006:974: zhing lpags kyi steng du bzhag la /
NK010(tha)006:975: he ru ka'i dam rgyas kha phru dbab /
NK010(tha)006:978: dang po phud kyis mi mchod du //
NK010(tha)006:979: dpal chen dkyil 'khor tshogs kyi bdag /
NK010(tha)006:980: bar du bshags pa mi bgyi ru //
NK010(tha)006:981: rnal 'byor ldan la dam tshig gnyan //
NK010(tha)006:982: tha ma bsgral bstab mi bgyi ru //
NK010(tha)006:983: rtogs pas bdag rgyud sngon bsgral phyir //
NK010(tha)006:984: da lta lhag mas mi mchod du //
NK010(tha)006:985: ma tshogs dbang phyug ging lang ka /
NK010(tha)006:986: pho nya sum brgya drug cu sogs //
NK010(tha)006:987: kun kyang dpal chen sprul pa yin //
NK010(tha)006:988: lhag ma kha chus mi bran du //
NK010(tha)006:989: dam tshig gcig tu bsre ba'i phyir //
NK010(tha)006:990: 'bangs thog rje yis mi mnan du //
NK010(tha)006:991: ci bcol las la bskul ba'i phyir //
NK010(tha)006:992: rje la 'bangs kyis mi rgol du //
NK010(tha)006:993: drag shul las thabs myur ba'i phyir //
NK010(tha)006:995: rnam dag rang bzhin zhi ba las //
NK010(tha)006:996: bcom ldan dpal chen sprul pa ni //
NK010(tha)006:997: thabs shes zla gsang rol pa las //
NK010(tha)006:998: dkyil 'khor mu ran skyong ba ste //
NK010(tha)006:999: khyed cag sngon gyi yal gam can //
NK010(tha)006:1000: lag na glo snying nang khrol thogs //
NK010(tha)006:1001: legs nyes stangs 'dzin tshogs khang nyul //
NK010(tha)006:1002: mthu dang rdzu 'phrul dpag tu med //
NK010(tha)006:1003: sngon tshe dpal chen he ru kas //
NK010(tha)006:1004: dug gsum r+au tra bsgral ba'i tshe //
NK010(tha)006:1005: khas blangs dam bcas dran gyis la //
NK010(tha)006:1006: srin mo'i za lam chen po ru //
NK010(tha)006:1007: pham phabs long la bstan pa srungs //
NK010(tha)006:1008: bcol ba'i phrin las 'grub par mdzod //
NK010(tha)006:1009: bdun pa thugs dam bskul pa ni /
NK010(tha)006:1011: mi gnas ye shes chos sku'i pho brang nas //
NK010(tha)006:1012: longs spyod rdzogs pa zhi dang khro bo'i lha //
NK010(tha)006:1013: thugs dam bskul lo 'gro ba'i don la dgongs //
NK010(tha)006:1014: rig pa'i rang bzhin bde gshegs snying po yang //
NK010(tha)006:1015: ma rig 'dzin pa'i kun gzhi lung ma bstan //
NK010(tha)006:1016: sgo lnga'i yul dang rten cing 'brel ba las //
NK010(tha)006:1017: rigs drug rgyud lnga'i gnas su 'khyams pa rnams //
NK010(tha)006:1018: las dang nyon mongs mthu yis gzir ba'i mthu //
NK010(tha)006:1019: phyi rol yul la smin pa'i sdug bsngal dang //
NK010(tha)006:1020: nad mtshon mu ge dgra bgegs 'byung po'i gdon //
NK010(tha)006:1021: 'jigs pa chen po brgyad dang bcu drug kun //
NK010(tha)006:1022: mngon spyod drag po'i rol pas tshar bcad nas //
NK010(tha)006:1023: log rtog dngos por zhen pa'i sems can rnams //
NK010(tha)006:1024: rgyu 'bras theg pa gzhan gyis gdul dka' bas //
NK010(tha)006:1025: rang byung ye shes rtogs pa'i phrin las mdzod //
NK010(tha)006:1026: brgyad pa chad tho bsgrag pa ni /
NK010(tha)006:1028: dus gsum rnam dag kun tu bzang po'i dus //
NK010(tha)006:1029: mngon rdzogs ye shes dam pa'i 'og min du //
NK010(tha)006:1030: kun gzhi yid chos dag pa'i ston pa yis //
NK010(tha)006:1031: rang snang rang bzhin med pa'i 'khor tshogs la //
NK010(tha)006:1032: rgyal ba dgongs brgyud rdzogs pa'i yo ga gsum //
NK010(tha)006:1033: brda tshig brjod pa bral bar bstan pa'i tshe //
NK010(tha)006:1034: grags chen gsal ba'i ston pa bcu gnyis dang //
NK010(tha)006:1035: dga' rab dpa' bo gsang 'dzin rdo rje chos //
NK010(tha)006:1036: brda brgyud rig 'dzin grub pa mchog rnams kyis //
NK010(tha)006:1037: ston 'khor dgongs pa gcig pa'i dbang thob bzhin //
NK010(tha)006:1038: tshogs brgyad rang grol gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK010(tha)006:1039: 'khrul pa gzhi la dag pa'i phrin las mdzod //
NK010(tha)006:1040: de rjes gsang sngags bstan pa byung ba'i tshe //
NK010(tha)006:1041: 'og min dga' ldan ri rab lhun po'i rtse //
NK010(tha)006:1042: lha gnas gsum du grags pa'i gnas mchog dang //
NK010(tha)006:1043: sham+b+ha la dang u rgyan za hor yul //
NK010(tha)006:1044: sing+ga la dang gnam lcags 'bar ba'i rtse //
NK010(tha)006:1045: mchod rten chen po bde byed brtsegs pa ru //
NK010(tha)006:1046: rig 'dzin sde snod mtha' dag babs pa'i tshe //
NK010(tha)006:1048: dkyil 'khor mu ran skyong ba thams cad kyis //
NK010(tha)006:1049: gtor ma len cing legs nyes stangs 'dzin pa'i //
NK010(tha)006:1050: khas blangs dam bca' bzhin du phrin las mdzod //
NK010(tha)006:1051: de rjes 'gro don dus la babs pa'i tshe //
NK010(tha)006:1052: klu sgrub snying po pad+ma thod phreng sogs //
NK010(tha)006:1053: grub pa'i rig 'dzin chen po brgyad rnams kyis //
NK010(tha)006:1054: 'dzam bu'i gling du dar zhing rgyas mdzad cing //
NK010(tha)006:1055: khyad par brag dmar dpal gyi mchims phu ru //
NK010(tha)006:1056: rig 'dzin slob dpon pad+ma 'byung gnas kyis //
NK010(tha)006:1057: lha sras rgyal po tshangs pa'i me tog la //
NK010(tha)006:1058: sgrub pa bka' brgyad dkyil 'khor zhal phyes shing //
NK010(tha)006:1059: seng ge rnam rol khas bu ri yi rtser //
NK010(tha)006:1060: gnod sbyin thams cad dam la bzhag pa'i tshe //
NK010(tha)006:1061: srog snying phul te chad tho bzung ba ltar //
NK010(tha)006:1062: mchod gtor bzhes la phrin las 'grub par mdzod //
NK010(tha)006:1063: de rjes tshogs bdun rol pa bal po'i yul //
NK010(tha)006:1064: rang snang mchod rten bya rung kha shor du //
NK010(tha)006:1065: rang byung rdo rje 'jigs med gling pa la //
NK010(tha)006:1066: dbyings kyi mkha' 'gros nam mkha' mdzod kyi brda //
NK010(tha)006:1067: ye shes lnga ldan sprul pa'i shog ser las //
NK010(tha)006:1068: brag dmar bre gu brtsegs pa'i dge'u ru //
NK010(tha)006:1069: kun tu bzang po dri med 'od zer gyis //
NK010(tha)006:1070: bka' rgya lung rdzogs gtad rgya bkrol ba'i tshe //
NK010(tha)006:1071: spyan gcig khrag tu khol ba'i ma mo dang //
NK010(tha)006:1072: bya rog gtsug phud 'dzin pa'i drang srong gis //
NK010(tha)006:1073: khas blangs tha tshig bzhin du phrin las mdzod //
NK010(tha)006:1074: dgu pa bshal chu gtor mar bran la brtan ma skyong ba ni /
NK010(tha)006:1076: tshogs dang bka' yi bdag nyid ni //
NK010(tha)006:1077: khrag 'thung rdo rje nam mkha'i yum //
NK010(tha)006:1078: gangs ri can gyi yul lha ni //
NK010(tha)006:1079: bdud dang gnod sbyin sman mo bzhi //
NK010(tha)006:1080: tshur spyon tshur spyon gtor ma longs //
NK010(tha)006:1081: rten 'brel yan lag bcu gnyis dang //
NK010(tha)006:1082: dus sbyor bcu gnyis gnas dag pas //
NK010(tha)006:1083: bal bod mtshams na tshe ring ma //
NK010(tha)006:1084: la stod rdo rje g.ya' ma skyong //
NK010(tha)006:1085: gnod sbyin gangs la kun bzang mo //
NK010(tha)006:1087: jo mo gangs rar spyan gcig ma //
NK010(tha)006:1088: byang na mkha' lding klu mo rgyal //
NK010(tha)006:1089: kha rag rdo rje khyung btsun ma //
NK010(tha)006:1090: rma chen spom rar drag mo rgyal //
NK010(tha)006:1091: kong btsun de mo bod khams skyong //
NK010(tha)006:1092: 'brog btsan rdo rje sman gcig ma //
NK010(tha)006:1093: jo mo nags rgyal dbyar mo bsil //
NK010(tha)006:1094: dbus na rdo rje zu le sman //
NK010(tha)006:1095: kun kyang pad+ma'i bka' nyan te //
NK010(tha)006:1096: dam la gnas shing rigs la 'go //
NK010(tha)006:1097: tha tshig bzhin du gtor ma long //
NK010(tha)006:1100: 'gong po spun dgu'i nad dal srungs //
NK010(tha)006:1101: rtag chad thar par 'khrul pa yi //
NK010(tha)006:1102: 'jig tshogs lta ba dbu mar bzlog /
NK010(tha)006:1103: bden don rnam pa bcu gnyis kyi //
NK010(tha)006:1104: bstan pa dar ba'i phrin las mdzod //
NK010(tha)006:1105: la la le le tam tam te te kha rak+ma ma ma sring 'gro ma h+aum b+h+yo h+aum h+aum /
NK010(tha)006:1106: bcu pa rta bro brdung ba ni /
NK010(tha)006:1107: gtor gzhong ri rab tu bsam pa kha sbub la /
NK010(tha)006:1109: dam sri bya ba'i sdig can khyod //
NK010(tha)006:1110: 'gro ba yongs kyi rgyud la rgol //
NK010(tha)006:1111: byang chub sems kyi brtul zhugs bros //
NK010(tha)006:1112: mnan no stong chen 'og tu mnan //
NK010(tha)006:1113: gtad do chu srin gre bar gtad //
NK010(tha)006:1114: bskyur ro gshin rje'i kha ru bskyur //
NK010(tha)006:1115: bsreg go ye shes me yis bsregs //
NK010(tha)006:1116: bdag tu lta ba ma zhig bar //
NK010(tha)006:1117: bskal pa zhig kyang mi gtang ngo //
NK010(tha)006:1119: bcu gcig pa dngos grub blang ba ni /
NK010(tha)006:1121: byin rlabs kun gyi rtsa ba bla ma ni //
NK010(tha)006:1122: dngos grub stsol phyir dpal chen rol ba'i lha //
NK010(tha)006:1123: rnam thar sgo gsum thugs kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK010(tha)006:1124: rang bzhin yongs grub byang chub sems kyi dngos //
NK010(tha)006:1125: phyag rgya chen po mchog gi dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)006:1126: sa bcu lam lnga dbang bcu phyi nang gnyis //
NK010(tha)006:1127: rig 'dzin bzhi dang sku lnga ye shes lnga //
NK010(tha)006:1128: grub chen brgyad dang phrin las rnam pa bzhi //
NK010(tha)006:1129: 'khor ba'i rang bzhin glo bur sgrib pa gnyis //
NK010(tha)006:1130: kun gzhi'i khams la bag la nyal gyi tshul //
NK010(tha)006:1131: shin tu rnam dag rnam kun mchog ldan gyi //
NK010(tha)006:1132: dngos grub dam pa deng 'dir stsal du gsol //
NK010(tha)006:1138: gtang rag gi mchod bstod phul la /
NK010(tha)006:1139: bcu gnyis pa bshags pa ni /
NK010(tha)006:1140: hoh sngags kyi dngos grub ma lus pa //
NK010(tha)006:1141: dam tshig nyid la brten gyur kyang //
NK010(tha)006:1142: rmongs dang ma rig nyon mongs pas //
NK010(tha)006:1143: zil gyis non pa bdag cag ni //
NK010(tha)006:1144: nyes pa du ma'i snod lags te //
NK010(tha)006:1145: mgon po thugs rje che rnams kyi //
NK010(tha)006:1146: thugs la khro ba mi mnga' yang //
NK010(tha)006:1147: legs nyes stangs 'dzin bdag po rnams //
NK010(tha)006:1148: skyon mthong tsam nas chad pa gcod //
NK010(tha)006:1149: 'gal zhing nongs pa ci mchis pa //
NK010(tha)006:1150: mthol lo bshags so tshangs par stsol //
NK010(tha)006:1151: yi ge brgya pa lan gsum gyis snying nas bshags par bya'o //
NK010(tha)006:1152: bcu gsum pa nyer bsdu ni /
NK010(tha)006:1154: snod bcud lha dang gzhal yas su //
NK010(tha)006:1155: shar ba dag pa'i snod bcud kyang //
NK010(tha)006:1156: rten nyid brten pa lha rnams kyang //
NK010(tha)006:1157: gtso bo la thim de yang h+aum //
NK010(tha)006:1158: zhabs kyu nas bzung n+aa da'i bar //
NK010(tha)006:1159: rim yal gdod ma'i gshis su a //
NK010(tha)006:1161: bcu gzhi pa spyod lam gyi rnal 'byor du ldang ba ni /
NK010(tha)006:1162: slar yang rig pa byang chub sems //
NK010(tha)006:1163: rjes thob gnyug ma'i he ru ka /
NK010(tha)006:1164: phyag rgya gcig pa'i gnas gsum du //
NK010(tha)006:1165: yi ge'i mtshan pas rnam rtog bsrung //
NK010(tha)006:1167: zhes rdo rje'i go bgo zhing yi ge brgya pas brtan par bya /
NK010(tha)006:1168: bco lnga pa bsngo smon ni /
NK010(tha)006:1170: snang grags rig pa dkyil 'khor gsum gyi ngang //
NK010(tha)006:1171: bsod nams ye shes rim gnyis rnal 'byor tshogs //
NK010(tha)006:1172: mi gnas ye shes mya ngan 'das par bsngo //
NK010(tha)006:1173: kun kyang dpal chen go 'phang thob par shog /
NK010(tha)006:1175: bcu drug pa bkra shis ni /
NK010(tha)006:1177: gdod ma'i mgon po rigs lnga gangs chen mtsho //
NK010(tha)006:1178: sku lnga lhun rdzogs sprul pa'i zhing khams la //
NK010(tha)006:1179: bskal bzang sangs rgyas stong rtsa 'byon pa yi //
NK010(tha)006:1180: sgron ma'i bskal pa bzang po'i bkra shis shog /
NK010(tha)006:1181: stong gsum mi mjed rdo rje theg pa'i zhing //
NK010(tha)006:1182: 'phur 'gro'i bstan pa 'byung gnas u rgyan yul //
NK010(tha)006:1183: gangs ri'i khrod du 'bod pa khri srong rjes //
NK010(tha)006:1184: thugs bskyed bstan pa mtha' rgyas bkra shis shog /
NK010(tha)006:1185: 'dzam gling sa yi lte ba rdo rje'i gdan //
NK010(tha)006:1186: pan grub chos rgyal 'dzom pa chos 'khor gsum //
NK010(tha)006:1187: mdo sngags bstan pa dar ba gangs can ljongs //
NK010(tha)006:1188: rgyal bstan yun du gnas pa'i bkra shis shog /
